You can open an existing document in order to Tidy it by following these simple
simple steps, below.

<div class="steps" markdown="1">

1. Use the **Open…** menu item in the **File** menu.

2. Drag a file in Finder to _Balthisar Tidy_’s icon in the Dock.

<% if boolENV('feature_supports_applescript') %>
3. Create an AppleScript program to tell Finder to open a file with
   _Balthisar Tidy_.
<% end %>

